org.openimaj.ml.clustering.assignment.soft

Class HierarchicalLongPathAssigner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.ml.clustering.assignment.soft.HierarchicalLongPathAssigner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assigner<long[]>, SoftAssigner<long[],double[]>

    public class HierarchicalLongPathAssigner
extends Object
implements SoftAssigner<long[],double[]>
    A SoftAssigner for gathering the clusters assigned to a point from a hierarchical clustering. The returned clusters represent the path down the tree to the final closest leaf node.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
